\intbl \ql 1. The programme conceptualization design is flawed. The programme is skewed towards cosmetology and not skin and body therapy. There appears to be a focus on the business aspects in this course and an apparent lack of the primary elements of the intended profession. The need for a skin and body therapist with more business knowledge must be evidenced to validate this claim and to support the rationale.\cell \pard 
\intbl \ql 1\cell \pard 

\intbl \row \pard 
\pard\trowd\trqc \trpaddl113\trpaddt113\trpaddb113\trpaddr113\trpaddfl3\trpaddft3\trpaddfb3\trpaddfr3\trgaph100\trrh100\trleft36
