\intbl \ql 2.  There is no core academic staff complement to provide academic leadership and support indicated in the application. Not all staff members have the relevant teaching experience and there are too few staff members with the required qualifications to teach in the field that should be the focus of the programme.  \cell \pard 
\intbl \ql 3\'2C 4\cell \pard 

\intbl \row \pard 
