\intbl \ql 3. There was Insufficient information submitted per site to determine whether adequate resources and infrastruture at the various sites are available to offer the programme. The programme needs more advanced equipment to be able to teach advanced therapies. \cell \pard 
\intbl \ql 7\cell \pard 

